{"tid":2006791,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"呢幾日TG公海有啲奇怪","createTime":"2020-05-08T04:23:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T05:56:19.000Z","uid":286685,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1370e0bcfcff69c3b1c68d192c31d7ae0ca2d844","tid":2006791,"uid":286685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T04:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DKTQWB9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDKTQWB9.jpg&h=e08c7f4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢幾日公海有啲奇怪；<br />\n有分別扮演最激的勇武 同 派膠的奇怪人士 製造分化，<br />\n又有唔同人在多個公海發fake news⋯ <br />\n仲有同一系列嘅人湧入某個group嘅奇景。<br />\n唔係捉鬼，亦唔係話用呢個ID嘅人全部有問題。不過對家知道我哋有鍾意將啲嘢浪漫化嘅傾向。<br />\nIf it was me, I would先係一個特定公海製造noise，再透過其他人散出去。<br />\n正正好似上面咁樣。<br />\n#大家睇路"},{"pid":"28c3fa3f970a611e33e3570e992f9e08349fa255","tid":2006791,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T04:27:21.000Z","msg":"希望多啲人改名做卡比<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ffac83f28c5e5dc07a8f85e5974f29b6f9211a","tid":2006791,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T04:32:08.000Z","msg":"好似波台手足同時事台咁做都搞得亂連登啦, 出面照辦煮碗有幾難"},{"pid":"5269beb2a2ccd3968466e1101aa80e6c99493b15","tid":2006791,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T05:56:19.000Z","msg":"講到口臭<br />\n貼連儂牆你都唔會係公海搵人搞啦<br />\n反而係開花會?"}]}